{"tid":2097123,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來連燈仔做左會計師幫大陸仔做假數","createTime":"2020-07-06T14:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:44:54.000Z","uid":41803,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4dec7424eb4b9492b383059f5f5a7c95c78aca3e","tid":2097123,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200706/DFLHDU2T5TOBCZAFPGS5XMCITU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200706%2FDFLHDU2T5TOBCZAFPGS5XMCITU%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=4e11ff7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200706%2FDFLHDU2T5TOBCZAFPGS5XMCITU%2F&h=265251ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200706/DFLHDU2T5TOBCZAFPGS5XMCITU/</a><br />\n<br />\n中匯安達半年添18公司客　一半涉可疑賬目　<br />\n問題股核數師　四折廉價搶客<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【財經專訪】內地手遊股雲遊（484）早前「DQ」核數師羅兵咸，換入中匯安達會計師樓。本報統計，今年至今已有18間上市公司改用中匯安達，其中九間涉停牌、報表有可疑等問題。中匯安達市佔率增加，執行合夥人施連燈接受本報專訪，自揭以市價四折收費搶客之謎，並指幫問題股核數並非問題。"},{"pid":"bba067f9c1e312f7357ecb2d1023389e96754232","tid":2097123,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"不嬲都收wok jobs啦"},{"pid":"65ad09fd9e26653f90b67418b7a643fd3912532a","tid":2097123,"uid":356218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"其實屙跌不嬲大把人放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你見到佢地咁搏盡都係圍威喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係個個喺度搵粒數咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527c46f7d4f39f7362c986455f8e04a52cf2ec70","tid":2097123,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"條友個樣點解可以咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><